Title: Gutting the Pool
Description:
The kobyss are... a bit larger than I expected, and I might--might, you understand?--have more trouble with them than I originally anticipated.

Kill any stupid fish-faces you see.
ObjectivesText: Kill 10 kobyss in The Hungering Pool in Hallowfall.
CompletionText: Yes, make them bleed. Make them pay!
RewardText:
You've killed a lot of them.

I wouldn't mind if you killed more. Just saying.
